FROM python:3.10-alpine
WORKDIR /code

COPY requirements.txt ./

RUN apk update && \
    apk add --no-cache --virtual .build-deps \
    build-base \
    gcc && \
    pip install --no-cache-dir --user -r requirements.txt && \
    apk del .build-deps && \
    rm -rf /root/* /tmp/*

COPY . .
ADD vktgbot .

CMD [ "python", "vktgbot" ]
